org.apache.flink.runtime.rpc.akka

类 AkkaInvocationHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.rpc.akka.AkkaInvocationHandler
  • 所有已实现的接口:

    直接已知子类:
    FencedAkkaInvocationHandler

    class AkkaInvocationHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.reflect.InvocationHandler, AkkaBasedEndpoint, RpcServer
    Invocation handler to be used with an AkkaRpcActor. The invocation handler wraps the rpc in a LocalRpcInvocation message and then sends it to the AkkaRpcActor where it is executed.
